              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "I am told that if you place a live frog in a pan of boiling water he jumps straight out. If, however, you place a live frog in a pan of cold water and bring it slowly to the boil the frog cooks…He becomes the victim of an exponential behaviour pattern that he had not appreciated.",
              "id": "1718215983066"
            },
