                    "text": "We have to somehow or other get our leg underneath us so that we can carry our selves. Our position is neither sitting nor standing, it is in-between. It is more like squatting. Many people find it difficult to squat in balance on the ground – never mind on a moving animal! This is our challenge!",
                    "id": "1491126431792"
