                    "text": "Ultimately we are what we think. We can have the best body and riding skills but unless we believe this we have nothing. Riding develops and tests our self control. Each moment we ride brings a new test. To ride really well we must learn to rise above all tests. We have to “know” riding in our mind and really trust ourselves to achieve our full riding potential. ",
                    "id": "1287903695549"
                  },
