                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "text": "To “know” we have to learn. We never stop learning. It is a lifetime’s task. We are constantly refining and improving our knowledge. This book aims to develop the concept of a \"Learning Rider\" and to help the reader to become one. A Learning Rider is a rider who is driven to perpetually deepen her understanding of the horse/rider interaction and to use that understanding for the benefit of all riders and horses.",
                    "id": "1360218104666"
